<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yào yáng jìng tā de chǎng, nǐ shì mài zi hái shì kāng,
 kāng yòng bù miè de huǒ shāo jǐn, mài zi yào shōu zài cāng,
 zhǔ shǒu lǐ ná zhe bǒ jī yáng, yuè bǒ mài zi yuè kào jìn zhǔ shēn páng,
 mài zi kāng bǐ yào fēn kāi, bì jīng dà fēng yáng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ yào yáng jìng tā de chǎng 迦南1383</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
